data.description: Nestled at the end of a peaceful cul-de-sac in Healdton, Oklahoma, this charming 3-bedroom, 1-bathroom home is a haven for those seeking the perfect blend of tranquility and convenience. Situated on nearly an acre of fully fenced land with a gated entry, you'll relish the privacy and security of this property. With a generous yard, you'll have plenty of room for outdoor activities, gardening, and relaxation. Park your boat or RV with ease under the dedicated carport, complete with a 110v connection. No more worries about storage or charging when adventure calls. In addition to the boat/RV carport, there's an attached carport for your daily drivers and a detached carport that can accommodate two more vehicles. Plus, there's a 10' x 19' storage area for all your tools and equipment. Gather around the fire pit on cool evenings, creating lasting memories with friends and family. And for those unpredictable Oklahoma storms, rest easy knowing there's a storm shelter ready to keep you safe. Commuting to Ardmore or downtown Healdton is a breeze, making this home the best of both worlds. Inside, the home boasts tile floors throughout, making for easy cleanup and a modern aesthetic. The large master bedroom with a walk-in closet provides ample space and storage for your comfort. This property offers the ideal backdrop for a serene, country lifestyle while still being within reach of all the amenities and services you need. Don't miss the opportunity to make this peaceful retreat your own. Schedule a viewing today and discover the serenity of country living at its finest.
